data.name: lblInstructions.Text
data.value: Itachi has been sent into the future. Your job is to help him beat the shooter and their boss. Press left and right to move him. Press space bar to jump. Once you get the Power-Up at the top platform, you can shoot by pressing the Z Key. When jumping and fallling, and shooting, remember to use strategy and time everything perfectly. You have 12 health, use them wisely.
